36:58.694 --> 37:00.392
Guy gave him
the location.

37:00.435 --> 37:03.569
What's in it?Drugs?

37:03.612 --> 37:05.266
Money.

37:05.310 --> 37:09.618
♪♪

37:09.662 --> 37:11.664
Why doesn't Pete
just do it himself?

37:11.707 --> 37:13.056
It's too tough
to get to.

37:13.100 --> 37:14.362
How tough?

37:14.406 --> 37:15.972
Ropes,
climbing gear.

37:16.016 --> 37:17.887
There's no way that Pete
and his gangbangers

37:17.931 --> 37:19.933
are rappelling
down mountainsides.

37:19.976 --> 37:21.674
Who else
is looking for it?

37:21.717 --> 37:23.980
For the next couple of days,just us.

37:24.024 --> 37:25.330
That's why
we need to act quick.

37:25.373 --> 37:28.376
We need to start first thing
tomorrow morning.

37:28.420 --> 37:31.031
♪♪

37:31.074 --> 37:32.119
Well,
we'll run it by Pope.

37:32.162 --> 37:35.078
If he's into it,
I'm into it.

37:35.122 --> 37:36.210
Alright.

37:36.254 --> 37:37.298
Yeah, me too.

37:37.342 --> 37:45.828
♪♪

38:06.762 --> 38:12.681
♪♪

38:12.725 --> 38:18.383
♪♪

38:18.426 --> 38:27.435
♪ So Sergeant Pepper
took you by surprise ♪

38:27.479 --> 38:29.394
♪♪

38:29.437 --> 38:37.445
♪ You better see right through
that mother's eyes ♪

38:37.489 --> 38:40.448
♪♪

38:40.492 --> 38:48.238
♪ Those freaks was right
when they said you was dead ♪

38:48.282 --> 38:51.416
♪♪

38:51.459 --> 38:59.380
♪ The one mistake you made
was in your head ♪

38:59.424 --> 39:01.991
♪♪

39:02.035 --> 39:11.261
♪ Ah, how do you sleep
at night? ♪

39:11.305 --> 39:17.050
♪♪

39:17.093 --> 39:24.666
♪ You live with straights
who tell you you was king ♪

39:24.710 --> 39:27.887
♪♪

39:27.930 --> 39:35.808
♪ Jump when your mama
tell you anything ♪

39:35.851 --> 39:38.941
♪♪

39:38.985 --> 39:46.601
♪ The only thing you done
was yesterday ♪

39:46.645 --> 39:49.648
♪♪

39:49.691 --> 39:57.612
♪ And since you're gone
you're just another day ♪

39:57.656 --> 40:00.223
♪♪

40:00.267 --> 40:09.407
♪ Ah, how do you sleep
at night? ♪

40:09.450 --> 40:19.373
♪♪

40:19.417 --> 40:29.427
♪♪

40:30.993 --> 40:33.039
[ Horn honks ]

40:33.082 --> 40:34.736
[ Dog barking ]

40:34.780 --> 40:39.045
[ Horn honks ]

40:42.483 --> 40:43.919
Bro.
Yo.

40:43.963 --> 40:47.009
What the hell are you doing?
Renn and Nick are asleep.

40:47.053 --> 40:49.534
Let's surf.What?

40:49.577 --> 40:50.883
Let's go surfing.

40:50.926 --> 40:53.886
Are you kidding?

40:53.929 --> 40:56.802
The pier lights are on.

40:56.845 --> 40:59.892
Bro, it's cold outside and
the pier lights aren't for shit.

40:59.935 --> 41:01.850
Come on!

41:04.505 --> 41:07.769
We could duct-tape these
to the front of the boards.

41:07.813 --> 41:09.945
Hmm?

41:09.989 --> 41:11.294
Alright.

41:11.338 --> 41:14.210
Alright, I'm coming.
Just lay off the horn.

41:17.997 --> 41:21.217
[ Screaming,
roaring on television]

41:35.841 --> 41:37.407
Why aren't you asleep?

41:37.451 --> 41:38.583
I was watching TV.

41:38.626 --> 41:40.367
Hmm.

41:42.848 --> 41:45.328
You smell good,
Aunt Birdie.

41:45.372 --> 41:47.940
Thank you.
That's my perfume.

41:52.901 --> 41:55.948
If you want pancakes
tomorrow,

41:55.991 --> 41:58.080
you need to find a place
to lay down.

42:03.869 --> 42:06.219
Come here, baby.

42:07.133 --> 42:09.875
It's okay.
I'll take care of your mama.

42:14.227 --> 42:15.445
Ugh.

42:15.489 --> 42:17.230
Can we just, mm,

42:17.273 --> 42:19.928
drop it for today,please?

42:19.972 --> 42:21.887
Mm.

42:23.715 --> 42:28.241
It was important that I come off
as a legit professional tonight.

42:28.284 --> 42:29.285
Mm-hmm.

42:29.329 --> 42:31.200
I was there
for business.

42:31.244 --> 42:32.245
Mm.

42:32.288 --> 42:35.248
Now they think
I'm as crazy as you.

42:40.514 --> 42:43.082
Tell me.

42:43.125 --> 42:49.262
Why do you even care
what they think?

42:52.657 --> 42:54.441
What's going on with you?

42:54.484 --> 42:56.530
Mm.
Hmm?

42:56.574 --> 42:59.402
You roll up here
with two kids,

42:59.446 --> 43:01.013
looking like you need
a meal yourself.

43:01.056 --> 43:04.059
No money, no crew.

43:04.103 --> 43:07.280
Out here just wilding.

43:07.323 --> 43:09.369
What the hell
is going on?

43:09.412 --> 43:11.414
Ugh.

43:11.458 --> 43:16.898
♪♪

43:16.942 --> 43:22.600
♪♪

43:22.643 --> 43:23.775
I don't know.

43:23.818 --> 43:27.256
♪♪

43:27.300 --> 43:32.044
Well, your two kids need you
to figure it out.

43:32.087 --> 43:41.053
♪♪

